            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 225ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
