      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>apple[s] </strong>(skin on) and discard the core[s]</p><p>Chop your <strong>mangetout</strong> roughly</p><p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>,<strong> </strong>then remove the <strong>outer leaves</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Shred the<strong> inner core</strong></p>",
