    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>gochujang </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span>[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong>, <strong>tamari soy sauce</strong> and most of your <strong>toasted sesame seeds </strong>(save some for garnish!) – this is your <strong>bulgogi-style sauce</strong></p>",
