    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu is crispy, add the <strong>grated apple </strong>and cook for 5 min or until the apple has started to softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>bulgogi-style sauce </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant<strong> </strong>– this is your<strong> bulgogi-style tofu</strong></p>",
