      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, top the rice with the <strong>chopped mangetout</strong> and put the lid back on for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p><p>Once warmed through, add the<strong> lettuce leaves</strong> and <strong>shredded core</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>cooked rice & mangetout</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> rice salad</strong></p>",
